================================================================================
Third-party assets — different licenses
================================================================================

The AGPL applies to the game *code* (anything under `src/`, `tools/`,
`index.html`, `styles.css`, and similar source files). The bundled assets
under `Ninja Adventure - Asset Pack/`, `assets/`, and `audio/` are
licensed separately as described below. These licenses are compatible
with redistribution alongside an AGPL-licensed program.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sprites, tilesets, and bundled sound effects
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Pack:    Ninja Adventure Asset Pack
  Authors: Pixel-boy  (https://pixel-boy.itch.io/)
           AAA        (https://www.instagram.com/challenger.aaa/)
  Pack page: https://pixel-boy.itch.io/ninja-adventure-asset-pack
  License: Creative Commons Zero (CC0 1.0 Universal) — public domain
           See `Ninja Adventure - Asset Pack/LICENSE.txt`.

The ambient sound effects `audio/wind.wav` and `audio/bird.wav` are taken
from the same Ninja Adventure Asset Pack (CC0).

